{
  "stem": "521.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then later on, after a week or two, there were some Germans came to watch over us, and we had to evacuate it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were about, I would say, 12 to 14 in one of those huts, which only was good only for about four people.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the reason we survived is because we were so many of us, and we were in-- we were lying in that hut as if, as sardines.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like the head was at the end and the feet was in the middle.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that's the way we were keeping warm.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Again, I was in a sleeping bag, and I had a very good protections.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't-- the sleeping bag was solidly protecting me, and the other people had one of those things, among other covers--",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Blankets.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Blankets we were sleeping on or-- or-- or-- or something else.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now anyway, we were here, and we went out to dig ditches.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were tank traps.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It means that the Russians against who couldn't be stopped when they were crossing over the car paths about 2,000 meters high-- which is about 2,000/6,000 feet high.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were supposed to be stop at the flat land between the Austrian and Hungarian border, so we were digging and digging.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now it went OK in December, but in January it became hard.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The land, the ground froze over, and it was just impossible to dig.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now the Germans knew it, but they were still yelling at us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Move!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Move!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And tempo!",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Tempo!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they insisted we should-- by that time we had axes, but the axes didn't work either because it was just digging into solid cement, or solid rock, or solid anything.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But we went out, and then we pretended that we are digging, so we were moving.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
